---
---

<section class="bg-[#1A1816] px-[10px] py-24">
  <div class="bg-[#22201E] rounded-3xl py-20 px-8 md:px-16 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Story -->
      <div data-animate>
        <p class="font-montserrat text-teal text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-4">Why We're Different</p>
        <h2 class="font-fraunces text-cream text-[clamp(32px,4vw,48px)] leading-[1.08] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-6">
          Built by a pharmacist.<br />
          Not a <em class="italic text-terracotta">startup playbook.</em>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-inter text-cream/50 text-base leading-[1.7]">
          <p>
            NovaMed wasn't built by engineers who read about healthcare. It was built by <strong class="text-cream/80">Dr. Jobby John, PharmD, FACA</strong> — a licensed pharmacist with nearly two decades in compounding pharmacy and personalized medicine.
          </p>
          <p>
            As the <strong class="text-cream/80">Immediate Past President of the Texas Pharmacy Association</strong>, JJ doesn't just understand compliance — he shaped the regulatory landscape that governs it. That expertise is baked into every protocol, every guardrail, every audit trail in the platform.
          </p>
          <p>
            Most platforms say "we take compliance seriously." We say: <strong class="text-cream/80">we enforce it</strong>. Our partners don't just get tools — they get the infrastructure to practice compounding-based care the right way.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Credentials + Stats -->
      <div data-animate data-delay="1">
        <!-- Credential Card -->
        <div class="bg-[#1A1816] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-cream/5 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="font-fraunces text-teal text-2xl">JJ</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-inter text-cream font-semibold text-lg">Dr. Jobby John</p>
              <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-sm">PharmD, FACA · CEO & Founder</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-teal text-sm">→</span>
              <span class="font-inter text-cream/50 text-sm">Immediate Past President, Texas Pharmacy Association</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-teal text-sm">→</span>
              <span class="font-inter text-cream/50 text-sm">UT Austin College of Pharmacy, Class of 2013</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-teal text-sm">→</span>
              <span class="font-inter text-cream/50 text-sm">20 years in compounding & personalized medicine</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-teal text-sm">→</span>
              <span class="font-inter text-cream/50 text-sm">National voice on AI in healthcare</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-[#1A1816] rounded-xl p-5 border border-cream/5 text-center">
            <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-3xl mb-1">37</p>
            <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-xs">State Licenses</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#1A1816] rounded-xl p-5 border border-cream/5 text-center">
            <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-3xl mb-1">NABP</p>
            <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-xs">Accredited</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#1A1816] rounded-xl p-5 border border-cream/5 text-center">
            <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-3xl mb-1">503A/B</p>
            <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-xs">Compliant</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#1A1816] rounded-xl p-5 border border-cream/5 text-center">
            <p class="font-fraunces text-teal text-3xl mb-1">~20yr</p>
            <p class="font-inter text-cream/40 text-xs">In Healthcare</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
